  "prompt": "What are the services provided by Five Boro Mold Specialist?",
  "response": "Five Boro Mold Specialist is a professional mold remediation company based in New York City. They offer a range of services related to mold inspection, testing, and removal. Here are the primary services they provide:\n\n1. **Mold Inspection and Testing**:  \n   - Comprehensive assessments to detect mold in residential and commercial properties.  \n   - Air quality testing and surface sampling to identify mold types and concentrations.  \n   - Use of advanced tools like moisture meters and infrared cameras to locate hidden mold.\n\n2. **Mold Remediation**:  \n   - Safe and effective removal of mold from affected areas.  \n   - Containment of contaminated areas to prevent cross-contamination.  \n   - Cleaning and sanitizing of surfaces and belongings.  \n\n3. **Water Damage Restoration**:  \n   - Addressing water damage to prevent mold growth.  \n   - Removal of standing water and drying of affected areas.  \n\n4. **Preventive Measures**:  \n   - Recommendations to prevent future mold growth, such as improving ventilation and controlling humidity.  \n   - Application of mold-resistant coatings and materials.  \n\n5. **Post-Remediation Verification**:  \n   - Follow-up inspections and testing to ensure mold has been fully removed.  \n   - Certification to confirm the property is mold-free.  \n\n6. **Asbestos Testing and Removal**:  \n   - Identification and removal of asbestos, which often coexists with mold in older buildings.  \n\nFive Boro Mold Specialist is known for adhering to industry standards, using environmentally friendly methods, and providing detailed reports to their clients. They are licensed and certified to handle mold-related issues in New York City.",
